[23/2012]
(9)  Despite subsection (8), where the Board has, in reliance on that subsection, computed the amount of contributions payable by a member or by an employer or a platform operator in respect of a member and the Board is notified subsequently, in such manner as the Board may require, of the date, month or year of birth of the member —
(
a
)
the Board may recompute the amount of contributions payable by the member, employer or platform operator, as the case may be; and
[Act 30 of 2024 wef 15/12/2024]
(
b
)
if the recomputed amount is higher than the amount that the Board computed originally —
(i)
the Board may issue to the member, employer or platform operator (as the case may be) a notice specifying the recomputed amount; and
[Act 30 of 2024 wef 15/12/2024]
(ii)
the member, employer or platform operator (as the case may be) must pay, within such time as is specified in the notice, the shortfall, in addition to the amount that the Board computed originally if not previously paid.
[23/2012]
[Act 30 of 2024 wef 15/12/2024]

