(
a
)
the securities account (if any) belonging to and in the sole name of the deceased designated shareholder; or
(
b
)
if the deceased designated shareholder does not have any securities account in his or her sole name, the securities account opened and operated by the personal representatives of the deceased designated shareholder on behalf and for the benefit of the estate of the deceased designated shareholder, if any.
(3)  The following is a discharge to the Board in respect of a designated shareholder’s vested shares:
(
a
)
the transfer of the vested shares under subsection (2)(
a
);
(
b
