a
)
the Board is notified that the designated shareholder has died and the designated shareholder has executed a memorandum under section 25(1) that provides for payment to a nominee in accordance with section 25(1)(
a
)(iii); or
(
b
)
a designated shareholder’s designated shares payments have been credited to the general moneys of the Fund under subsection (7)(
b
) and the Board is satisfied that the designated shareholder is still alive.
