b
)
where the nominee of a deceased designated shareholder has died on or after the designated shareholder’s death — the nominee’s personal representatives; or
(
c
)
where the deceased designated shareholder died before 1 January 1996 or did not execute a memorandum under section 25(1) — the designated shareholder’s personal representatives.
[Act 39 of 2021 wef 01/04/2022]

